		<content:encoded><![CDATA[If you identify a narrative technology that isn’t listed here, please <a href="https://env-1120817.us.reclaim.cloud/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">propose a new term for WonderCat</a>!

<hr />

[table id=1 /]]]></content:encoded>
		<excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[]]></excerpt:encoded>
		<wp:post_id>135</wp:post_id>
		<wp:post_date><![CDATA[2024-06-13 17:53:13]]></wp:post_date>
		<wp:post_date_gmt><![CDATA[2024-06-13 17:53:13]]></wp:post_date_gmt>
