<h1 class="editor-visual-editor__post-title-wrapper edit-post-visual-editor__post-title-wrapper">Final Project</h1>
<p id="block-230ff185-a9a4-4d37-a05a-327e9f390f96" class="block-editor-rich-text__editable block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-paragraph rich-text" role="document" aria-label="Block: Paragraph" data-block="230ff185-a9a4-4d37-a05a-327e9f390f96" data-type="core/paragraph" data-title="Paragraph" data-empty="false" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content">You've written four posts this semester. We looked closely at stories, films, and music. Throughout this experience, I have encouraged you to capture and share your responses to creative works that you are experiencing for the first time. As we conclude the semester, I want to give you an opportunity to revisit the creative works you've experienced and expand on the discoveries you made through the first three assignments.</p>
<p id="block-45916289-0f32-4eb7-b159-0db6cb479c77" class="block-editor-rich-text__editable block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-paragraph rich-text" role="document" aria-label="Block: Paragraph" data-block="45916289-0f32-4eb7-b159-0db6cb479c77" data-type="core/paragraph" data-title="Paragraph" data-empty="false" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content">Since the start of the semester, our course website has been set to private, meaning that only the students enrolled in the course can see the site. You have chosen between publishing your work (making it visible to your classmates) or keeping it private (so only I can see it). At the end of the semester, I will make our entire website public and you can choose to have your posts included in that public site (visible to anyone who finds our website) or set to private (still only visible to me). You also have the option of setting a password for any posts that you want to be able to share with family and friends only.</p>

<h2 id="block-d63b6f26-7059-441b-b3b1-bbae2028c8ab" class="block-editor-rich-text__editable block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-heading rich-text" role="document" aria-label="Block: Heading" data-block="d63b6f26-7059-441b-b3b1-bbae2028c8ab" data-type="core/heading" data-title="Heading" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content">Part 1: Collaborate on a Timeline</h2>
<p id="block-8240141c-105a-43b9-9689-16beecff98f3" class="block-editor-rich-text__editable block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-paragraph rich-text" role="document" aria-label="Block: Paragraph" data-block="8240141c-105a-43b9-9689-16beecff98f3" data-type="core/paragraph" data-title="Paragraph" data-empty="false" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content">I want you to take the technologies you identified in the first four assignments and prepare a selection for inclusion in our timeline. We'll start this work together in class (we'll be creating our timeline with <a href="https://timeline.knightlab.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">this tool</a>), but you'll need to do additional research on the technologies you experienced so you can enter the earliest iteration of that technology on the timeline as well. For each assignment, you will have identified at least one technology of creation and one technology of distribution/access/discovery. Select three of these to include on our timeline. I also want you to do research to find an earlier iteration of those technologies and create an event on the timeline for each of these as well. Each of your entries on the timeline should include clear citations to reliable sources. Each entry will ideally be accompanied by an openly licensed featured image (or a copyrighted image that can be included under fair use). We will use a shared google sheet to gather all of the components for this project and I may need to adjust for technical issues as they emerge. All details will be in our doc.</p>
<p id="block-ec0b743c-2b65-4b56-8017-01898cc45941" class="block-editor-rich-text__editable block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-paragraph rich-text" role="document" aria-label="Block: Paragraph" data-block="ec0b743c-2b65-4b56-8017-01898cc45941" data-type="core/paragraph" data-title="Paragraph" data-empty="false" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content"><strong>Technologies of Creation</strong>: The particular technique used by a creator. Occasionally, the technology you experienced was the first ever use of the technology, but more often the technology will have been used by many artists since its invention. Drawing on WonderCat (and most likely some additional research), your task will be to figure out how long that technology has been around and try to find the earliest iteration of it. Here are some examples from our semester:</p>

<ul id="block-a60c0d0d-3350-4d98-862f-d58c31a10129" class="block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-list block-editor-block-list__layout" role="document" aria-label="Block: List" data-block="a60c0d0d-3350-4d98-862f-d58c31a10129" data-type="core/list" data-title="List" data-is-drop-zone="true">
 	<li id="block-d0cf43b0-dc2d-4aa0-9794-a4b720cdad6b" class="block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-list-item block-editor-block-list__layout" role="document" aria-label="Block: List item" data-block="d0cf43b0-dc2d-4aa0-9794-a4b720cdad6b" data-type="core/list-item" data-title="List item">
<div class="block-editor-rich-text__editable rich-text" role="textbox" aria-label="List text" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content">The <a href="https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q25397095" target="_blank" rel="noopener">sandbox game</a> is a technology that allows players to play in a game world with very few rules or goals. It has been around since the late 1980s.</div></li>
 	<li id="block-aec15aaf-8412-423c-b0b9-859fcbf86d91" class="block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-list-item block-editor-block-list__layout" role="document" aria-label="Block: List item" data-block="aec15aaf-8412-423c-b0b9-859fcbf86d91" data-type="core/list-item" data-title="List item">
<div class="block-editor-rich-text__editable rich-text" role="textbox" aria-label="List text" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content">The <a href="https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q1321123" target="_blank" rel="noopener">plot twist</a> is a plot technology that is used in many stories (novels, plays, films, games, etc.). It has been around since ancient Greece.</div></li>
</ul>
<p id="block-547bf7ea-3b2f-480c-87bd-1825bbd0bff1" class="block-editor-rich-text__editable block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-paragraph rich-text" role="document" aria-label="Block: Paragraph" data-block="547bf7ea-3b2f-480c-87bd-1825bbd0bff1" data-type="core/paragraph" data-title="Paragraph" data-empty="false" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content"><strong>Technologies of Distribution/Access/Discovery</strong>: The technology that helped you find or experience a creative work. This can be many different things, but here are some examples from our semester (I was able to locate each one in Wikidata and I'd like you to try to do the same):</p>

<ul id="block-16102254-a3c2-4a6e-ae10-c4a178de7286" class="block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-list block-editor-block-list__layout" role="document" aria-label="Block: List" data-block="16102254-a3c2-4a6e-ae10-c4a178de7286" data-type="core/list" data-title="List" data-is-drop-zone="true">
 	<li id="block-c2cc0b3b-4315-4c58-b880-cc71fa13e8c9" class="block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-list-item block-editor-block-list__layout" role="document" aria-label="Block: List item" data-block="c2cc0b3b-4315-4c58-b880-cc71fa13e8c9" data-type="core/list-item" data-title="List item">
<div class="block-editor-rich-text__editable rich-text" role="textbox" aria-label="List text" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content">YouTube's algorithm recommended a video that led you to a game or film or album. This is an <a href="https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q559856" target="_blank" rel="noopener">online video platform</a> as a technology of discovery. YouTube was not the first to do this, but it was one of the earliest.</div></li>
 	<li id="block-945f912e-14b4-482b-9113-70282045d3d9" class="block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-list-item block-editor-block-list__layout" role="document" aria-label="Block: List item" data-block="945f912e-14b4-482b-9113-70282045d3d9" data-type="core/list-item" data-title="List item">
<div class="block-editor-rich-text__editable rich-text" role="textbox" aria-label="List text" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content">A gaming platform (Steam) made it possible for you to buy a game for your PC. This is digital distribution as a technology of distribution (you also need an Internet-connected device, which is the technology of access).</div></li>
 	<li id="block-b91d0ab0-edbc-419f-aac9-e32221735675" class="block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-list-item block-editor-block-list__layout" role="document" aria-label="Block: List item" data-block="b91d0ab0-edbc-419f-aac9-e32221735675" data-type="core/list-item" data-title="List item">
<div class="block-editor-rich-text__editable rich-text" role="textbox" aria-label="List text" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content">I went to a movie theater to see the movie <em>Conclave</em>. The <a href="https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q41253" target="_blank" rel="noopener">movie theater</a> is a specific kind of auditorium where people gather to experience a creative work together (and usually the building contains multiple auditoriums facing multiple screens). This is simultaneously a technology of distribution and access. This sort of building is distinct from the <a href="https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q11183017" target="_blank" rel="noopener">open-air theater</a> used in Greek theatrical practices, but in the same tradition.</div></li>
 	<li id="block-5eb512d0-cc45-41f2-a4a0-0b55cc3c14b3" class="block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-list-item block-editor-block-list__layout" role="document" aria-label="Block: List item" data-block="5eb512d0-cc45-41f2-a4a0-0b55cc3c14b3" data-type="core/list-item" data-title="List item">
<div class="block-editor-rich-text__editable rich-text" role="textbox" aria-label="List text" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content">The recommendation stickers at Best Video helped you find a movie to watch. This is recommendation stickers in <a href="https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q1756711" target="_blank" rel="noopener">video rental shop</a> as a technology of discovery.</div></li>
 	<li id="block-23df1da8-e886-43e5-8700-55c094d23d0f" class="block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-list-item block-editor-block-list__layout" role="document" aria-label="Block: List item" data-block="23df1da8-e886-43e5-8700-55c094d23d0f" data-type="core/list-item" data-title="List item">
<div class="block-editor-rich-text__editable rich-text" role="textbox" aria-label="List text" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content">The genre section at Merle's Record Rack helped you find a movie to watch. This is <a href="https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q188451" target="_blank" rel="noopener">music genre</a> as a technology of discovery and it has been around at least since Aristotle.</div></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="block-e92c5d75-01a8-4642-aab1-c0bddc26beeb" class="block-editor-rich-text__editable block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-heading rich-text" role="document" aria-label="Block: Heading" data-block="e92c5d75-01a8-4642-aab1-c0bddc26beeb" data-type="core/heading" data-title="Heading" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content">Part 2</h2>
<p id="block-b158ee41-80f7-49b4-b060-a17fa76d752f" class="block-editor-rich-text__editable block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-paragraph rich-text" role="document" aria-label="Block: Paragraph" data-block="b158ee41-80f7-49b4-b060-a17fa76d752f" data-type="core/paragraph" data-title="Paragraph" data-empty="false" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content">After you've contributed to the timeline we're building together, I want you to create something on your own that you can share with our class or with the general public. This is your chance to dig even deeper into an issue you've discovered this semester and share the results of your research with all of us. I have two suggestions on how you can do this, but I'm open to other possibilities!</p>

<h3 id="block-279e28c4-d115-4024-92df-2691372b3d24" class="block-editor-rich-text__editable block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-heading rich-text" role="document" aria-label="Block: Heading" data-block="279e28c4-d115-4024-92df-2691372b3d24" data-type="core/heading" data-title="Heading" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content">A physical version of our Timeline for display on the third floor of Harugari Hall</h3>
<p class="block-editor-rich-text__editable block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-heading rich-text" role="document" aria-label="Block: Heading" data-block="279e28c4-d115-4024-92df-2691372b3d24" data-type="core/heading" data-title="Heading" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content">(You can create this by hand or I can get a digital file you create printed in color on 11x17 paper).</p>

<ul id="block-8cc1dc2b-2ebd-4efd-bd3b-b6f41f34c42e" class="block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-list block-editor-block-list__layout" role="document" aria-label="Block: List" data-block="8cc1dc2b-2ebd-4efd-bd3b-b6f41f34c42e" data-type="core/list" data-title="List" data-is-drop-zone="true">
 	<li id="block-b1056cd6-3b5f-4afd-9988-d18a1a2bfd96" class="block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-list-item block-editor-block-list__layout" role="document" aria-label="Block: List item" data-block="b1056cd6-3b5f-4afd-9988-d18a1a2bfd96" data-type="core/list-item" data-title="List item">
<div class="block-editor-rich-text__editable rich-text" role="textbox" aria-label="List text" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content">Focus on a single decade or some other unit of time (our timeline will cover all of human history :))</div></li>
 	<li id="block-84e1ad57-6c6b-44b1-8001-7e4e935049ee" class="block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-list-item block-editor-block-list__layout" role="document" aria-label="Block: List item" data-block="84e1ad57-6c6b-44b1-8001-7e4e935049ee" data-type="core/list-item" data-title="List item">
<div class="block-editor-rich-text__editable rich-text" role="textbox" aria-label="List text" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content">Focus on a single type of creative work (music, text, film, game, etc.)</div></li>
 	<li id="block-2ffefe87-be6d-4037-960c-90a664497607" class="block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-list-item block-editor-block-list__layout" role="document" aria-label="Block: List item" data-block="2ffefe87-be6d-4037-960c-90a664497607" data-type="core/list-item" data-title="List item">
<div class="block-editor-rich-text__editable rich-text" role="textbox" aria-label="List text" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content">Focus on a single genre of a single type of creative work (horror film, romance novel, sandbox game, etc.)</div></li>
 	<li id="block-62e5fc3d-08e7-4267-8006-db3ae5f2667e" class="block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-list-item block-editor-block-list__layout" role="document" aria-label="Block: List item" data-block="62e5fc3d-08e7-4267-8006-db3ae5f2667e" data-type="core/list-item" data-title="List item">
<div class="block-editor-rich-text__editable rich-text" role="textbox" aria-label="List text" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content">Some other focus!</div></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="block-d710eb0b-daec-48be-809d-f474940c2906" class="block-editor-rich-text__editable block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-heading rich-text" role="document" aria-label="Block: Heading" data-block="d710eb0b-daec-48be-809d-f474940c2906" data-type="core/heading" data-title="Heading" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content">Two or more of your posts revised for publication on our course website</h3>
<ul id="block-0dbc10aa-6146-458d-9b96-7979c29ad3b2" class="block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-list block-editor-block-list__layout" role="document" aria-label="Block: List" data-block="0dbc10aa-6146-458d-9b96-7979c29ad3b2" data-type="core/list" data-title="List" data-is-drop-zone="true">
 	<li id="block-2c8c021e-d657-4d69-9ef5-8496c151836b" class="block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-list-item block-editor-block-list__layout" role="document" aria-label="Block: List item" data-block="2c8c021e-d657-4d69-9ef5-8496c151836b" data-type="core/list-item" data-title="List item">
<div class="block-editor-rich-text__editable rich-text" role="textbox" aria-label="List text" data-wp-block-attribute-key="content">All images properly attributed</div></li>
 	<li id="block-1997b087-aba2-4cc4-b63a-419e98fabe7f" class="block-editor-block-list__block wp-block wp-block-list-item block-editor-block-list__layout" role="document" aria-label="Block: List item" data-block="1997b087-aba2-4cc4-b63a-419e98fabe7f" data-type="core/list-item" data-title="List item">
