		<content:encoded><![CDATA[In our shared Word Online document, please enter the following information from your draft post

Literary Work you're writing about

Experiences you had while reading (up to three)

For each experience, which of the following elements of narrative do you think caused the experience?

What technique do you think the creator used to prompt that experience?]]></content:encoded>
