		<content:encoded><![CDATA[Our glossaries are constantly growing with user-proposed terms! If you want to propose a new experience, technology, or benefit term, please visit <a href="https://forms.newhaven.edu/view.php?id=379445" target="_blank" rel="noopener">our term-proposal form</a>.]]></content:encoded>
